After searching for a simple command-line tool for uploading files to pastebin.com and finding none to be satifying, preseting pasteit:
A shell script that allows you to directly upload files to pastebin.com using their public api http://pastebin.com/api.php. 

For comments, bug reports, suggestions and love mails contact prakash(daught)mohan(yat)kdemail(daught)net or ssivrk007(yat)gmail(daught)com.
